    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, i get why people say that, but isn't it also true that the alternative—just letting judges decide based on what they think is \"evolving\" or \"fair\" today—is basically just making up the law as they go? if they aren't using the original meaning, wouldn't that be even more political/subjective?",
